copy?&#8221; asks neighbor Jill, and Chad does it.&#160;</p><p style=3D"col=
or: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0=
;">&#8220;Chad my boy, how about helping me develop some drugs?&#8221; asks=
 neighbor Jim, and he does.</p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-siz=
e: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>The neighbors are so=
