=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); text-decoration: underline;">How to Predict the=
 Future</a></em><span>. It&#8217;s all about trusting the curve, specifical=
ly, about trusting </span><strong>hardware curves</strong><span>.</span></p=
><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; ma=
rgin: 0 0 20px 0;">In 1996, Hertling plotted modem speeds to predict that s=
treaming video would be possible in 2005. Nine years later, in February 200=
