 line-height: 1.16em; margin: 1em 0 0.625em 0; position: relative;"><strong=
>The Goldilocks Zone</strong></h3><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-=
size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">There are two extreme p=
aths ahead for AI:&#160;</p><ol style=3D"margin-top: 0; padding: 0;"><li st=
yle=3D"margin: 8px 0 0 32px;"><p style=3D"box-sizing: border-box; color: rg=
b(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0; margin-bottom=
: 0; padding-left: 4px;">One path is the one we&#8217;ve been discussing: t=
hat we get AGI soon, then ASI soon thereafter, and humans quickly lose cont=
rol to greater intelligences. At the very least, whichever government contr=
ols the models that jump from AGI to ASI will win.</p></li><li style=3D"mar=
gin: 8px 0 0 32px;"><p style=3D"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(54, 55, =
55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0; margin-bottom: 0; paddi=
ng-left: 4px;">On the other extreme, this is all a bubble that&#8217;s boun=
d to pop as people realize AI isn&#8217;t actually going to get that much b=
etter. We won&#8217;t create AGI, and NVIDIA tanks.&#160;</p></li></ol><p s=
tyle=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin:=
 0 0 20px 0;"><span>But there is a third way, the </span><strong>Goldilocks=
 Zone</strong><span>: we get increasingly smart and capable helpers without=
 eliminating the need for humans, or birthing beings that have any desire t=
o eliminate humans.&#160;</span></p><p style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); fon=
t-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><em><strong>That is t=
he implication of agreeing with Leopold&#8217;s curve but disagreeing with =
the mapping.</strong></em><span> It&#8217;s what you get when you believe i=
n straight lines on a graph without believing in sci-fi.&#160;</span></p><p=
 style=3D"color: rgb(54, 55, 55); font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margi=
n: 0 0 20px 0;">In this view of the world, humans have a big role to play: =
we are the one who prompts.&#160;</p><div class=3D"captioned-image-containe=
